 • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Ambassador of China to South Africa, Lin Songtian, will host a media briefing at the Chinese Embassy in Pretoria on Friday. The Chinese government believes that due to the effective prevention and control efforts implemented across China, the COVID-19 epidemic has generally been brought under control. However, there is also a surge in the spread of the epidemic in other countries including South Korea, Japan, Italy, Iran. The first case of coronavirus in South Africa was confirmed on Thursday afternoon.